<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
     S05  PHYSICAL MODELING
═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section id="s05">
<div class="section-inner">
<div class="section-header hidden stagger-1">
<div class="section-number">05 / PHYSICAL MODELING</div>
<h2>Physical Modeling</h2>
<p class="section-thesis">Simulate the physics of vibration.</p>
</div>
<div class="card hidden stagger-2 mb-24">
<h3>The Plucked String</h3>
<p class="info-text mb-24">Click anywhere on the string to pluck it at that position. The pluck point shapes the initial harmonic balance — plucking at the center emphasises odd harmonics; plucking near the bridge adds brightness by exciting higher partials. Material determines the decay envelope and filter character.</p>
<div class="canvas-wrap mb-24" style="cursor:crosshair;">
<canvas height="120" id="string-canvas" onclick="pluckString(event)" style="width:100%;height:120px;" width="700"></canvas>
</div>
<div class="two-panel" style="gap:32px;">
<div class="controls">
<div class="control-row">
<span class="control-label">Material</span>
<div class="btn-row" id="string-material-btns">
<button class="btn btn-sm active" onclick="setStringMaterial('nylon',this)">Nylon</button>
<button class="btn btn-sm" onclick="setStringMaterial('steel',this)">Steel</button>
<button class="btn btn-sm" onclick="setStringMaterial('glass',this)">Glass</button>
<button class="btn btn-sm" onclick="setStringMaterial('crystal',this)">Crystal</button>
</div>
</div>
<div class="control-row">
<span class="control-label">Tension</span>
<input id="string-tension" max="3.0" min="0.3" oninput="document.getElementById('string-tension-val').textContent=parseFloat(this.value).toFixed(2)" step="0.05" type="range" value="1.0"/>
<span class="control-value" id="string-tension-val">1.00</span>
</div>
<div class="control-row">
<span class="control-label">Pluck Position</span>
<input id="string-pluck" max="0.99" min="0.01" oninput="document.getElementById('string-pluck-val').textContent=Math.round(this.value*100)+'%'" step="0.01" type="range" value="0.3"/>
<span class="control-value" id="string-pluck-val">30%</span>
</div>
<div class="btn-row">
<button class="btn" onclick="pluckStringAuto()">▶ PLUCK</button>
<button class="btn" id="bow-btn" onclick="toggleBow()">BOW MODE</button>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div class="note-text">
<strong style="color:var(--green);">Karplus-Strong algorithm (1983):</strong> a short noise burst fed into a delay line with a one-pole lowpass filter in the feedback path. The delay length sets pitch; the filter averages adjacent samples, simulating the energy loss of a real string. Remarkable acoustic realism with minimal computation — still used in modern physical modeling engines.
        </div>
<div class="info-text mt-16" style="font-size:13px;">
          String materials: <span class="highlight">Nylon</span> — warm, fast decay, rolled-off highs.
          <span class="highlight">Steel</span> — bright sustain, strong attack.
          <span class="amber-text">Glass</span> — fragile, bell-like overtones.
          <span class="amber-text">Crystal</span> — long sustain, ethereal shimmer.
        </div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
     S06  HISTORY TIMELINE
═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section id="s06" style="min-height:auto;padding-bottom:80px;">
<div class="section-inner">
<div class="section-header hidden stagger-1">
<div class="section-number">06 / HISTORY</div>
<h2>A Century of Synthesis</h2>
<p class="section-thesis">Every waveform solved a problem.</p>
</div>
<div class="hidden stagger-2">
<div class="timeline-scroll">
<div class="timeline-track">
<div class="timeline-line-h"></div>
<!-- 1: Theremin -->
<div class="timeline-node">
<div class="timeline-above">
<div class="tl-year">1919</div>
<div class="tl-name">Theremin</div>
<div class="tl-desc">First electronic instrument. Continuous sine waves shaped by hand proximity.</div>
</div>
<div class="timeline-dot"></div>
</div>
<!-- 2: Hammond Organ -->
<div class="timeline-node">
<div class="timeline-below">
<div class="tl-year">1935</div>
<div class="tl-name">Hammond Organ</div>
